</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="63" type="taxonomic remarks">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="63">Taxonomic remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="63">
<bibRefCitation author="Paulian, R" journalOrPublisher="Revue Francaise d'Entomologie" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" pagination="113 - 118" refId="B27" refString="Paulian, R, Cambefort, Y, 1991. Remarques sur le genre Helictopleurus et description de trois nouvelles especes (Coleoptera, Scarabaeidae). Revue Francaise d'Entomologie 13: 113 - 118" title="Remarques sur le genre Helictopleurus et description de trois nouvelles especes (Coleoptera, Scarabaeidae)." volume="13" year="1991">Paulian and Cambefort (1991)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName genus="H." lsidName="H. peyrierasi" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" rank="species" species="peyrierasi">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">H. peyrierasi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from Zombitsy, south-western Madagascar. 
<bibRefCitation author="Montreuil, O" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" pagination="373 - 376" refId="B20" refString="Montreuil, O, 2005b. Contribution a l'etude du genre Helictopleurus d'Orbigny, 1915. Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France 110: 373 - 376" title="Contribution a l'etude du genre Helictopleurus d'Orbigny, 1915." volume="110" year="2005 b">Montreuil (2005b)</bibRefCitation>
, after having examined specimens collected in nearby Kirindy, and having compared them with the type specimens of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Fairmaire" baseAuthorityYear="1899" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Helictopleurus fungicola" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fungicola">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">Helictopleurus fungicola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, treated this taxon as a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName genus="H." lsidName="H. fungicola." pageId="0" pageNumber="63" rank="species" species="fungicola.">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">H. fungicola.</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
We compared the type specimens of the nominotypical subspecies with those of 
<taxonomicName genus="H." lsidName="H. fungicola subsp. peyrierasi" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" rank="subSpecies" species="fungicola" subSpecies="peyrierasi">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">H. fungicola peyrierasi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and found significant differences, especially in the shape of male genitalia, that support the original treatment of 
<taxonomicName genus="H." lsidName="H. peyrierasi" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" rank="species" species="peyrierasi">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">H. peyrierasi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
stat. rest. as a full species within the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Orbigny" authorityYear="1915" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Helictopleurus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">Helictopleurus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
